### Hybrid search (default)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "bill payment",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Full-text search only
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "invoice total amount",
  "search_mode": "fulltext",
  "top_k": 10
}

### Vector search only
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "payment due date",
  "search_mode": "vector",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Search with tag filter
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "bill",
  "search_mode": "hybrid",
  "filters": {
    "tags": ["bill"]
  },
  "top_k": 10
}

### Search with file type filter
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "document content",
  "filters": {
    "file_type": "pdf"
  },
  "top_k": 5
}

### Search documents (not pages)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "travel expenses",
  "search_target": "documents",
  "search_mode": "fulltext",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Hybrid search with custom weights
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "monthly bill",
  "search_mode": "hybrid",
  "hybrid": {
    "combination_method": "rrf",
    "rrf_k": 60,
    "weights": {
      "fulltext": 0.3,
      "vector": 0.7
    }
  },
  "top_k": 10
}

### Full-text search with fuzzy matching
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "paymnt",
  "search_mode": "fulltext",
  "fulltext": {
    "enabled": true,
    "fuzzy": {
      "enabled": true,
      "max_edits": 2,
      "prefix_length": 3
    }
  },
  "top_k": 5
}

### Search with multiple content fields
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "bill details",
  "search_mode": "hybrid",
  "include_content_fields": ["content", "content_markdown"],
  "top_k": 5
}

### List vector indices
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/search/indices
